				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Two FD'ers should be able to isolate the boss. Just have the necro intiate agro and begin training the pack and a secondary necro or SK agro the boss from the pack and FD. The initial necro would lead the others away and FD. Both necros would remain FD at this point until the mobs forgot them, afterwhich the mobs would just stand where they were.
<br />

<br />
