				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Guild helped me with this, wolves are super high ac, people could barely hit.  Everything else was hittable.  I think all the steps could be done in about an hour, it took us about an hour and a half and I wasn't 100% sure on all the steps and looking it up as we went along.  
<br />

<br />

<br />
We hold epic day events for stuff they is 1-3 groupable and either random on who gets help, or just do what we can with who we have.  Seems a good way to help people.  Was dreading this, due to passing on almost all my epic pieces to other necros, minus the slime blood (was only necro there at the time).
<br />

<br />

<br />
So if your looking to do this, get ya around 2 groups or so for speed of kills and you should be able to knock it all out in around an hour.  So its not too long that you'll have trouble getting people to help you.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
